hopobject.body: What's the exchange rate for euros? barkbox heavy chewer Glorifying violence against journalists is a shrewd move. Personally, I'm desensitized to the disrespect often shown toward my profession. For instance, I wasn't deeply outraged last weekend, when some idiots at Oklahoma State University took steak knives to an effigy of Thayer Evans, the Sports Illustrated writer who had aired the dirty laundry of OSU's football program.
